<lb n="2" break="no"/>ḍa<unclear>ḷē</unclear>svara Arirāyavibhāḍa bhāṣege tappuvarāyara gaṁḍa śrīvīrahariyappoḍeyaru
<lb n="3"/>prithvīrājyaṁgeyyuttirddalli Eṟagana 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>haḷḷiya kalligauḍana maga cikkataṁmanu mūḍaṇabeṭṭadalli Asahāyasūranāgi koḍali
</p>

<!--<h4>Third Section.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yalli kaḷḷara huydu keḍahi tānu bidda kāraṇakke Ātana tamma kēta(ṁ)ṇna huysida vīragallu maṁgaḷa
<lb n="6"/>mahāśrī śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
